! Changelog

|!Version |!Date |!Changes |
|0.1.19 |2026-04-27 |Declare soft-dependents `doc-template`, `file-pipeline` in plugin.info |
|0.1.18 |2026-04-14 |Video body template: inline `<video>` player with thumbnail-first cascade, quality selector (defaults to smallest downscale), resizable wrapper. Shared `fu-render-video-player` procedure. Video metadata extraction via `ffprobe` (date, GPS, dimensions, duration, codec, device). Video EXIF field mapping |
|0.1.17 |2026-04-14 |Binary upload route (`/api/file-upload-binary`): streams raw file to disk, no base64/size limit. Upload progress overlay with percentage. Drag-over highlight CSS. Video subfolder routing (`video/*` → `videos/`). Fix `deleteDerived` for non-default locations + clean empty `_derived/` parent. Replace `magick.exe` with `magick` (native WSL) |
|0.1.16 |2026-04-09 |Pass dropzone `prop-system-prompt`, `prop-provider`, `prop-model` to pipeline client for LLM step overrides |
|0.1.15 |2026-04-09 |file-pipeline integration: `<$file-dropzone>` auto-detects file-pipeline plugin and triggers `pipeline="auto"` on every upload. New `pipeline` attribute ("auto", "<name>", "none"). `upload.js` skips `runProcessor()` when file-pipeline installed. Settings UI shows "configure via file-pipeline" hint for thumbnail settings |
|0.1.14 |2026-04-08 |Fix rename: preserve file directory on rename instead of re-routing by MIME type. Fix thumbnail URI: derive from canonical URI instead of guessing prefix. Use last title segment as filename on rename |
|0.1.13 |2026-04-08 |Add test coverage: uri-resolver, upload/delete/rename route validation, dropzone widget (44→100 jasmine specs) |
|0.1.12 |2026-04-07 |Cleanup: replace \define with \function for thumb-state, replace hardcoded colors with palette variables |
|v0.1.11 |2026-04-07 |Add `target-prefix` attribute to `<$file-dropzone>`: inserts path prefix between subfolder and filename on disk, exposed as variable in action string for tiddler title construction |
|v0.1.10 |2026-04-07 |EXIF extraction: auto-extract metadata from uploaded images via ImageMagick and map to tiddler fields. Configurable global field mapping + per-location overrides. Extracts date, camera, dimensions, GPS, exposure, lens. Enabled by default. |
|v0.1.9 |2026-04-07 |Fix thumbnail cascade: position filter first in ViewTemplateBodyFilter chain (some third-party plugins break cascade evaluation for subsequent filters). Fix draft deletion: skip draft tiddlers in file cleanup to prevent accidental file deletion when cancelling editor. Remove redundant `all[current]` from cascade filter (`:cascade` already provides input title) |
|v0.1.8 |2026-04-07 |Location registry: multi-location support with writable/read-only flag, uri-resolver library, artifact cascade (delete/rename propagates to `_artifact_source` tiddlers), location management UI in settings, `location` attribute on `<$file-dropzone>`, `serve-location` route for user-created locations, optional integration with scattered-binaries and llm-connect |
|v0.1.7 |2026-03-27 |Remove phantom file-paths filter from docs, deduplicate helpers in dropzone.js, bundle default media-types shadow tiddler |
|v0.1.6 |2026-03-15 |Add null guards to th-saving-tiddler and th-renaming-tiddler hooks |
|v0.1.5 |2026-03-15 |Add name field to plugin.info |
|v0.1.4 |2026-03-15 |Add regression tests, CI test gate, and extract helpers library |
|v0.1.3 |2026-03-15 |Fix th-deleting-tiddler hook: return tiddler instead of true to preserve hook chain, add null guard for upstream hooks returning undefined |
|v0.1.2 |2026-03-12 |Add allowed media types section to settings UI, fix missing media-types config causing all uploads to be rejected (415), fix thumbnail generation failing for filenames with spaces (quote paths in processor commands), update dev-workflow docs |
|v0.1.1 |2026-03-06 |Standardize plugin tabs: add documentation/changelog/license to list, replace license.tid with LICENSE.md.meta sidecar |
|v0.1.0 |2026 |Initial release |
